name: Zaza Weed Dispensary
description: Weed dispensary in busy Walking Street of Pattaya. Here you can buy cannabis products and also chill at our lounge, listen to music, play Playstation 5.

products_flowers.name: Pink Runtz
products_flowers.description: Like Black Runtz, Pink Runtz is a phenotype of the OG Runtz strain but blended with a slightly different mix of Zkittlez and Gelato parent strains.

products_flowers.name: Dosidos Skittlez
products_flowers.description: Do-Si-Dos Zkittlez was made by crossbreeding Do-Si-Dos with Watermelon Zkittlez plants. It‚Äôs stimulating, thanks to a high dose of THC, with a fruity and creamy flavor, but when smoked in high quantities, it helps with muscle relaxation and produces a heavy stoned effect.

products_flowers.name: Blue Sunset Sherbet
products_flowers.description: Blue Sunset Sherbet gets its genetics from Purple Punch and Sunset Sherbet. It‚Äôs a beautiful strain with a sweet, berry flavor and a high THC level that can reach up to 27%. If you‚Äôre looking for an indica that will help you relax and feel euphoric, this is a perfect choice.

products_flowers.name: Buddha Kush
products_flowers.description: This strain is perfect for evening use as it will help you relax and drift off to sleep.

products_flowers.name: Gelato Dreams
products_flowers.description: Gelato Dream is a cross between Gelato 41 and Loud that features a sweet, aromatic ice cream flavor and one of the highest THC concentrations on the market. It‚Äôs known for its characteristic purple color and many resin crystals that are sure to fight depression and lift your mood.
